    "Evaluation": {
      "text": "Generally a clinical diagnosis, however comorbidity is common so additional work-up/screening is required:\nLabs:\nSerum glucose\nSerum ethanol\nCBC\nMetabolic panel\nLFTs\nCK\nDrug screen if concern for coingestion\nImaging:\nCXR\nin all patients (pneumonia is most common infection)\nConsider\nhead CT\nif evidence of head trauma, focal deficits, or other concerning findings\nConsider\nLP\nif concern for meningitis",
      "subsections": {},
      "tables": [],
